body:
The thing about Detective Pikachu’s designs, now that I’m thinking about it, is that they’re exactly what these pokemon would look like if they were real and nobody actually wanted that and I’m slowly making peace with that fact

I still think Pikachu’s tail was done wrong but that’s my opinion

summary: It’s so funny how just because the Pokémon in the new movie have textures now (cause let’s be honest, nothings changed that much...
body: It’s so funny how just because the Pokémon in the new movie have textures now (cause let’s be honest, nothings changed that much about them. They just got realistic textures), it’s all of a sudden “gritty” or “grimdark” when the trailer was a light-hearted and sweet one.
